summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 8263, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley between blocks twenty-five (25) and Twenty-six (26), Pontius Third Addition to the City of Seattle, by grading the same, and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
